it
is
for
a
legend
to
arise
in
a
lonely
countryside!
I
examined
him
as
to
the
reasons
for
his
weird
belief.
It
seems
that
from
time
to
time
sheep
have
been
missing
from
the
fields,
carried
bodily
away,
according
